"n.远地点 【考】 反义词：perigee(近 地点) 【记】 apo(远)+gee(地球)→ 远离地球的点→远地点 【同】 同根词：geology(地 质学)，gee=geo n. 远地点(太阳、月球或人造卫星轨道上离地球中心最远的点) 【例】The orbit has an apogee of 200 miles from the earth 这个轨道最远点在离地球200英里的地方. 【记】apo远, gee = geo地球－远离地球－远地点 【参】geology(n 地质学) 【反】perigee(n 近地点) 【记】apo + g 地球重力加速度，地球, geo 【相关】perigee 近地点，geology 地质学 apogee (n.)  ""point at which the moon is farthest from the earth,"" 1590s, from French apogée, from Latin apogaeum, from Greek apogaion, neuter adjective, ""away from the earth,"" a term from Ptolemaic astronomy, from apo ""off, away"" (see apo-) + gaia/ge ""earth"" (see Gaia). Adjective forms are apogeal, apogean."
